{"tid":2064700,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【seed呢屌你老母？！！！】 難怪金與正氣炸！空飄傳單驚見李雪主拍AV　脫北者喊冤","createTime":"2020-06-15T04:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T03:25:13.000Z","uid":242537,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a14bb5fd21b4ee1bc1868bccf6753f72d9e964bf","tid":2064700,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:01:38.000Z","msg":"國際中心／實習編輯葉定豊報導<br />\n<br />\n北韓領導人金正恩的胞妹、勞動黨第一副部長金與正，近日針對脫北者團體以大氣球散發批評金正恩傳單一事，放狠話嗆「現在是時候與南韓決裂」，並提及了武力挑釁的可能性，引起國際關注。至於金與正生氣的原因，似乎是金正恩夫人李雪主被南韓空飄傳單合成為日本AV封面，對此南韓也禁止脫北者對南韓發傳單。<br />\n<br />\n對網路上流傳的脫北者對北韓空飄文宣中可以看到，李雪主的臉被合成在身穿性感服裝的日本AV女優上，而男主角則和已故南韓總統盧武鉉合成；脫北者還在日文標題下方，特別用韓文註明「雪主的愛」，並備註「李雪主拍A片，難道只有金正恩知道，北韓人民卻都不知道？」、「李雪主夫人脫個精光，火辣辣地和幹部拍攝令人羞恥的影片來賺外匯？」。這張照片不但掀起北韓高層、民眾的怒火，也讓南韓盧武鉉感到不滿。除此之外，傳單內容還批評金正恩是弒兄的殺人魔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/04/27/1337402-XXL.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F1337402-XXL.jpg&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8m6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=efe31b94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F1337402-XXL.jpg&h=23e87ed8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/04/27/1337402-XXL.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n據韓媒報導，南韓政府為了平息眾怒，依《南北交流協力法》、《航空安全法》、《公有水面法》對脫北團體「自由北韓運動聯盟」提告，不過該組織的代表朴尚學（박상학）反駁，網路上流傳的傳單是7年前其他團體施放的文宣，而自己組織長期施放的文宣內容，都是在批評北韓金氏政權等議題，「我們原訂在6月25日空飄的百萬傳單，內容也都是關於韓戰（北韓軍隊南侵）的真相，以及金正恩十大罪惡事蹟。」懷疑是有心人士刻意挑撥脫北者團體與南韓政府的關係。<br />\n<br />\n經南韓《世界日報》確認，合成李雪主頭相的空飄傳單，其實是2013年10月朴槿惠時代，由平壤市民會、BLUEUNION等極右派（極端保守派）團體所施放的。"},{"pid":"9aa1db5ff19ac2f51cf21ffb4dab6ccef5ddeac1","tid":2064700,"uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/15/2609297-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2F2609297-XXL.jpg&h=8504c2db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7755148aeb3791fcc28c4d8067dfcc6506d5622","tid":2064700,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200427/331460707692449792.jpeg/SSekrL6YS1uRZIoSrJ8HZ6r1O-ktgyMKf57OSn-ezko?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200427%2F331460707692449792.jpeg%2FSSekrL6YS1uRZIoSrJ8HZ6r1O-ktgyMKf57OSn-ezko%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=b296fcd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85634072d80854dbc6e3dff44cedff6789224702","tid":2064700,"uid":270308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a7755148aeb3791fcc28c4d8067dfcc6506d5622","tid":2064700,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200427/331460707692449792.jpeg/SSekrL6YS1uRZIoSrJ8HZ6r1O-ktgyMKf57OSn-ezko?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200427%2F331460707692449792.jpeg%2FSSekrL6YS1uRZIoSrJ8HZ6r1O-ktgyMKf57OSn-ezko%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=b296fcd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:05:09.000Z","msg":"01正仆街"},{"pid":"9f7ac9e01f0fc6b4a00150fa300aac2f2a8e399d","tid":2064700,"uid":68689,"like":7,"dislike":24,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"香港都有唔少<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z513vjp.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZ513vjp.jpg&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8m6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=0cac37e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/Z513vjp.jpg</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWGECkSO.png&amp;h=df14a713&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/134619_da8093977da5eb1095c78431cd699ede.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.e